    "description": "<p>These… things… served as blank canvasses for the Green Lords' flesh-weaving. Once they were kept carefully locked away in laboratories and breeding pits; now, with their creators gone all these years, who knows where they might be found? Command one in the tongue of the Green Lords and it might obey — or accept you as its master. It grows by consuming the living, and can split off smaller copies of itself.</p>",
